    "body": "![success_simple](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/4312421/1064749/d627627e-134c-11e3-81fe-23e969c73237.GIF)\n\nHi Jakobgager,\n\nthanks a lot !\n- If I  put The final $  on a new line, then it is the markdown that doesn't work.\n- but if I let it on the last line with an intermediate SPACE, \"\\end{pmatrix} $\", the miracle happens.\n\n$\\begin{pmatrix}\n2 & 3 & 1 \\\n0.5 & 2 & -1 \\\n-1 & 5 & -7\n\\end{pmatrix} $\n"
